name: Sophia

name: James

name: Isabella
career: Isabella is known for blending high fashion with urban culture. Her work has been featured in many prominent streetwear collections. She constantly pushes the boundaries of fashion to merge luxury and street style.

name: Olivia
career: Olivias designs bring together bohemian style and glamour in a unique way. Her collections often mix flowy fabrics with bold embellishments. She is adored by celebrities for her red carpet looks.

name: Amelia

name: Mia

name: Eli

name: Aubrey

name: Sofia
career: Sofias designs are known for their elegance and timeless appeal. She often uses luxurious fabrics and intricate detailing. Her work is a staple in high-end fashion circles.

name: Jackson

name: Avery

name: Savannah
career: Savannahs designs are inspired by bohemian fashion with a luxurious touch. Her collections feature rich fabrics and relaxed silhouettes. She is a favorite among those who value comfort and style.

name: Victoria
career: Victoria specializes in glamorous evening wear with a modern twist. Her designs are known for their dramatic flair and luxurious fabrics. She continues to push the boundaries of formal fashion.
